Package org.openhab.binding.lcn.logic.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LCNChannel
    This class represents an IP connection.
    LCNChannelList
    This class represents a list of LCNChannels.
    LCNInputModule
    Represents a LCN Module that delivers input (e.g. a sensor).
    LCNInputModule.EngineStatus
    Represents the states of a single engine.
    LCNInputModule.LEDInfo
    A simple class to represent the state of different LEDs.
    LCNInputModule.SceneData
    Special data class for light scenes.
    LCNInputModule.Threshold
    Special data class for thresholds.
    LCNItemBinding
    This class represents a single Item, Connection tuple with additional information about the underlying LCNCommand.
    LCNItemMap
    This class maps ItemBindings on openHAB commands.
    LCNModule
    Simple (abstract) data class, which represents a LCN module and its current state.
    LCNOutputElement
    Data class that combines LCNChannels and an output buffer for that channel.
    LCNSyntax
    This class defines most of the LCNSyntax, its identifiers etc.
